msg":"比人屌下個屎眼就搵到"},{"pid":"143384ffee0437d3e3c9ed78d63921242105f76f","tid":1486190,"uid":117409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:13:18.000Z","msg":"光復完香港就搵到"},{"pid":"453840f9dc68cf718d576428567d0055fc4240aa","tid":1486190,"uid":139409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T20:25:10.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnf9O7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbnf9O7G.jpg&h=5ee9af01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=ecec5deb\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=ecec5deb\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"7a89d5ba79e8020e541bfe8357acd112da94f480","tid":1486190,"uid":122516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T21:09:46.000Z","msg":"首要條件，靚仔靚女"},{"pid":"b098bf9a49d0c592c67be707890849df79e611d2","tid":1486190,"uid":38633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T22:37:34.000Z","msg":"have faith, whatever will be will be<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-lzNg3-7sjI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-lzNg3-7sjI&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsstNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=fc3c2797\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-lzNg3-7sjI</a>"},{"pid":"1ecfaa5967d58fd958c208374c5b066275b5e41e","tid":1486190,"uid":217108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc804447f3966dec0293b51b47e76e8c44bffc20","tid":1486190,"uid":75156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:53:03.000Z","msg":"充實自己人生啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:41:03.000Z","msg":"充實人生只會係有錢家庭先講得出口<br />\n一般人都要為口奔波"},{"pid":"1c869717c26ad2b6be36e3558b7c1aa6d49bfeed","tid":1486190,"uid":266336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T23:41:53.000Z","msg":"毒撚有冇機（往骨子裡毒果種）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\